> give bottle to charlotte

"Is that... whisky? I never imagined." Charlotte accepts the bottle, takes off the cap, and sniffs it one or twice. "Yes, perhaps this will help me forget... or help me not to feel anymore. Thank you. I will retire to my suite, but perhaps I'll see you again after a catnap. I suspect I'll be hungry afterward."

Charlotte clutches the bottle in her hands and heads up the stairs to the upper deck.
Perhaps Charlotte is finished napping.
